messages.message: Hi I’m trying to use AILabs-UAT through API and it seems I do not have access. Can someone help?
@Gwen are you trying to call AI Labs environment or AI Hub UAT environment? Can you share the URL of the environment?
it would be great to get granted for both https://aihub.uat.instabase.com/ and https://aihub.instabase.com
You can sign in using IB account via Google sign up directly.

@Varun Jain I acquired a piece of code from Matt in order to send prompts from Instabase.com (http://Instabase.com) to AIHub.UAT. It currently requires an API token, and we are currently using his token and this works.

We currently need this code to run another POV. What I did was I generated my own Token through the profile page (https://aihub.uat.instabase.com/apps/admin/users/gwen.wong/profile) and it appears that my Account/Token does not have ‘a licence’. Is there a way to turn this on at all?
